The project provides low level hardware drivers to access EV3 sensors and actuators.
It also includes some example applications.

Assumptions:
1> Used development environment is linux.
2> The tools require to be executed in bash environment.

Requirements:
1> ARM cross compiler for EV3
2> The setup environment expects the following linux utilities to be installed
	> expect
	> pv
	> sshpass

References:
1> http://www.robotnav.com/ev3/

